# Pocket Creature Character Sheet (Fan Tool)

A small browser-based character sheet / helper for a tabletop-style creature-collecting game.
Runs locally in your browser (static HTML/CSS/JS + JSON data).

## What this is
- A **fan-made utility** for managing character/party data.
- A **static site** (no server) intended for personal use and small groups.

## What this is not
- **Not an official product**.
- **Not affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by** Nintendo, Game Freak, or The Pokémon Company.
- **Not a game client**, ROM, emulator, or distribution of any game files.

## IP / Trademark Notice
Pokémon and related names are trademarks of Nintendo, Game Freak, and The Pokémon Company.
This repository is a **non-commercial fan project** and is provided for **educational and personal use**.

## Content Policy (important)
To reduce IP risk, this project intentionally does **not** include:
- Game sprites, official artwork, screenshots, anime/manga panels
- Audio/music from official games/shows
- ROMs, ISO files, save files, or decrypted game assets
- Datamined proprietary assets or text dumps from commercial releases

If you fork or contribute, please avoid adding the above.

## Data Disclaimer
Any creature names, move names, or ability names that appear are used only for
identification/reference in a fan context. If you prefer, you can replace names
with your own original setting terminology.

